snippet: Novak Djokovic has vowed not to become over-confident as he seeks to extend a 15-match winning streak when he returns to action in Dubai, his first tournament since winning a sixth Australian Open title last month....
lead_paragraph: Novak Djokovic has vowed not to become over-confident as he seeks to extend a 15-match winning streak when he returns to action in Dubai, his first tournament since winning a sixth Australian Open title last month.

headline.print_headline: Djokovic Determined Not to Get Carried Away With Success
headline.main: Djokovic Determined Not to Get Carried Away With Success
